data.text:
List of famous people who died in Bognor Regis, with photos when available. These notable Bognor Regis deaths are loosely ordered by how famous each person was, meaning the most well-known people are at the top of the list. Some of the people mentioned below were celebrities who died in Bognor Regis, while others were just renowned in their line of work. Either way everyone on this list has Bognor Regis listed as their official place of death in any public records. Each prominent person who passed away in Bognor Regis has information about them next to their names, including the year they were born and their place of birth.

People include everyone from Moore Marriott to C.M. Pennington-Richards.

If you're trying to answer the questions, "Which famous people died in Bognor Regis?" and "Which celebrities died in Bognor Regis?" then this list will have you covered.

This list of historic deaths in Bognor Regis includes athletes, musicians, celebrities and notable local figures.
